  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Chop your <strong>waxy potatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Peel and grate (don't chop!) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>'Nduja</strong> into small pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1651675013455-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1651675013455-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1651675013455-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1651675013455-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1651675013455-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>halved potatoes</strong> to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Add <strong>half</strong> your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>(save the rest for later!) with the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, a pinch of <strong>sugar </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together so the potatoes are evenly coated</p><p>Put the baking tray in the oven for 25-30 min or until the potatoes are tender and lightly charred, then set aside to cool slightly – these are your <strong>balsamic roast potatoes</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1651675020304-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
